Escape from Anathema Mines
=====================================================================
(c) 2005 Phil Hassey, see COPYING for details
http://www.imitationpickles.org/ld486/ - for contest details, etc
=====================================================================

Story
-----
You've been a slave for too long, escape the
Anathema mines!

Controls
--------
left, right - change direction
up, down - run forward / backward
ctrl - turn on/off flashlight

enter, p, space - pause
escape - quit

Instructions
------------
Pick up batteries for more power, turn off flashlight to
 - hide from guards
 - conserve battery power

Scoring
-------
Get points for collecting batteries, finishing the level quickly,
and having left over battery power.